item.title: Data Science in Action in Response to the Outbreak of COVID-19
item.description: This webinar series aims to promptly disseminate the newest data science methods, tools, and findings in response to the outbreak of COVID-19, facilitate the exchange of research ideas, and engage collaborations between data scientists and field experts worldwide to solve the COVID-19 crisis.
